function info($str) { echo "INFO: $str\n"; }
function warn($str) { echo "WARNING: $str\n"; }
function err($str) { die("FATAL ERROR: $str\n"); }

	err('You need PHP Version 7.0 to update to this version');
}

if (is_file('userdata/database/oidplus_empty.accdb') && (sha1_file('userdata/database/oidplus_empty.accdb') != '538cf05f6bf279f333cb8367db18ffb80725fa30')) {
	warn('File was created by someone else. Will overwrite the changes now: userdata/database/oidplus_empty.accdb');
	$tmp = pathinfo('userdata/database/oidplus_empty.accdb');
	$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('userdata/database/oidplus_empty.accdb')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
	warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
	if (!@copy('userdata/database/oidplus_empty.accdb', $backup_name)) {
		warn('Creation of backup failed');
	}
}
writefile_1();
if (!is_file('userdata/database/oidplus_empty.accdb')) {
	warn('File cannot be created (not existing): userdata/database/oidplus_empty.accdb');
} else if (sha1_file('userdata/database/oidplus_empty.accdb') != '538cf05f6bf279f333cb8367db18ffb80725fa30') {
	warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): userdata/database/oidplus_empty.accdb');
} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('userdata/database/oidplus_empty.accdb', 0644)) {
	warn('Could not change file permissions of userdata/database/oidplus_empty.accdb');
}

if (is_file('userdata/database/oidplus_empty.db') && (sha1_file('userdata/database/oidplus_empty.db') != '56847d80e35634c6e4d534d821c7c87b85283a5a')) {
	warn('File was created by someone else. Will overwrite the changes now: userdata/database/oidplus_empty.db');
	$tmp = pathinfo('userdata/database/oidplus_empty.db');
	$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('userdata/database/oidplus_empty.db')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
	warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
	if (!@copy('userdata/database/oidplus_empty.db', $backup_name)) {
		warn('Creation of backup failed');
	}
}
writefile_2();
if (!is_file('userdata/database/oidplus_empty.db')) {
	warn('File cannot be created (not existing): userdata/database/oidplus_empty.db');
} else if (sha1_file('userdata/database/oidplus_empty.db') != '56847d80e35634c6e4d534d821c7c87b85283a5a') {
	warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): userdata/database/oidplus_empty.db');
} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('userdata/database/oidplus_empty.db', 0644)) {
	warn('Could not change file permissions of userdata/database/oidplus_empty.db');
}

if (is_file('userdata/database/oidplus_example.accdb') && (sha1_file('userdata/database/oidplus_example.accdb') != 'd052287b7aa5ae36803db526b2659af5210a736f')) {
	warn('File was created by someone else. Will overwrite the changes now: userdata/database/oidplus_example.accdb');
	$tmp = pathinfo('userdata/database/oidplus_example.accdb');
	$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('userdata/database/oidplus_example.accdb')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
	warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
	if (!@copy('userdata/database/oidplus_example.accdb', $backup_name)) {
		warn('Creation of backup failed');
	}
}
writefile_3();
if (!is_file('userdata/database/oidplus_example.accdb')) {
	warn('File cannot be created (not existing): userdata/database/oidplus_example.accdb');
} else if (sha1_file('userdata/database/oidplus_example.accdb') != 'd052287b7aa5ae36803db526b2659af5210a736f') {
	warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): userdata/database/oidplus_example.accdb');
} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('userdata/database/oidplus_example.accdb', 0644)) {
	warn('Could not change file permissions of userdata/database/oidplus_example.accdb');
}

	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('U1FMaXRlIGZvcm1hdCAzABAAAQEAQCAgAAAAAwAAACYAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAoAAAAEAAAAAAAAAAAAAAABAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAADAC5PfQ0P+AAQA7cADrcPuw02DnoM5At3DK0JjAs4BzgJVwZ3BRoGNgO3BNUAAAAAAAAAAAAA'));

if (is_file('userdata/database/oidplus_example.db') && (sha1_file('userdata/database/oidplus_example.db') != 'afc8312e90f67fa2a5d629254f8ee4983086b9bb')) {
	warn('File was created by someone else. Will overwrite the changes now: userdata/database/oidplus_example.db');
	$tmp = pathinfo('userdata/database/oidplus_example.db');
	$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('userdata/database/oidplus_example.db')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
	warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
	if (!@copy('userdata/database/oidplus_example.db', $backup_name)) {
		warn('Creation of backup failed');
	}
}
writefile_4();
if (!is_file('userdata/database/oidplus_example.db')) {
	warn('File cannot be created (not existing): userdata/database/oidplus_example.db');
} else if (sha1_file('userdata/database/oidplus_example.db') != 'afc8312e90f67fa2a5d629254f8ee4983086b9bb') {
	warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): userdata/database/oidplus_example.db');
} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('userdata/database/oidplus_example.db', 0644)) {
	warn('Could not change file permissions of userdata/database/oidplus_example.db');
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplusBaseConfig.class.php');
	writefile_7();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusBaseConfig.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusBaseConfig.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusBaseConfig.class.php') != 'cc7ef95050dd4028116493a45e361da7b833916d') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusBaseConfig.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplusBaseConfig.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplusBaseConfig.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusBaseConfig.class.php') !== 'cc7ef95050dd4028116493a45e361da7b833916d') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusBaseConfig.class.php') !== '70ccf2c4be2ff87cfb42c560869da05cc8bcb398') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusBaseConfig.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplusBaseConfig.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplusBaseConfig.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusBaseConfig.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_7();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusBaseConfig.class.php') !== 'cc7ef95050dd4028116493a45e361da7b833916d') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusBaseConfig.class.php');
		}
	}
}

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php') != '038750342cd9159aac9ffe718b911e8fe9720cab') {

	}

	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php') !== '038750342cd9159aac9ffe718b911e8fe9720cab') {

		}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php');
	writefile_9();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php') != '61617c389722eb038cd22189236d8886ef7e47c9') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php') !== '61617c389722eb038cd22189236d8886ef7e47c9') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php') !== '65fa7e496bcd73bcaf4bd53200a4ac27fecdadb2') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_9();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php') !== '61617c389722eb038cd22189236d8886ef7e47c9') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php');

	}
}

if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	writefile_10();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') != '6bd183adde954cad9723dd63dc4f4dab5459e913') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== '6bd183adde954cad9723dd63dc4f4dab5459e913') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== '7860c317faf8b1989712958c7e328d1906711ee1') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_10();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== '6bd183adde954cad9723dd63dc4f4dab5459e913') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
		}
	}
}

		if (@sha1_file('userdata/database/info.txt') !== '816c096a9e7aa37227a6009d36f7e5de0160544b') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: userdata/database/info.txt');
			$tmp = pathinfo('userdata/database/info.txt');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('userdata/database/info.txt')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('userdata/database/info.txt', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_11();
		if (@sha1_file('userdata/database/info.txt') !== 'e22a354cab3284ee63ecf38228b2cb2200cc027d') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): userdata/database/info.txt');
		}
	}
}


file_put_contents('.version.php', "<?php // Revision 1177\n");
if (trim(@file_get_contents('.version.php')) !== '<?php // Revision 1177') err('Could not write to .version.php!');


echo 'DONE'; // This exact string will be compared in Update v3

@unlink(__FILE__);
if (is_file(__FILE__)) warn('Could not delete '.basename(__FILE__).'! Please delete it manually');
